<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ش ش:</span> <span class="c2">(الْبَشَاشَةُ)</span> طَلَاقَةُ الْوَجْهِ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(بَشَّ)</span> بِهِ يَبَشُّ بِالْفَتْحِ. وَرَجُلٌ هَشٌّ بَشٌّ أَيْ طَلْقُ الْوَجْهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>